                     <interp inst="t17790915-7-off33" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silver tea-spoon, value 18 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17790915-7-victim134" type="victimName">
                           George
                            Waddington
                        <interp inst="t17790915-7-victim134" type="surname" value="Waddington"></interp>
